http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: South Dakota Physical Education Content Standards

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The South Dakota Health Education Standards includes the standards/goals, indicators, benchmarks, and sample grade level objectives/activities. The standards are organized into grade level clusters so that a parent, local school board member, classroom teacher, or administrator could quickly review what physical education concepts are expected at a specific grade level. Grade level clusters are organized K-2, 3-5, 6-8, and 9-12.
